data.description: Traditional Brick Residence featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, bonus room, office, theater room in over 3500sf on 1.37 unrestricted acres with year-round mountain views. Easy paved access to the door. Gentle yard with mature landscaping and raised beds. Low maintenance brick exterior. Grand entry with open stairwell, beautiful railings, tall ceilings, and lots of natural light. As well as a coat closet, 1/2 bath, dining and office as you enter. The main living boasts extensive moldings, hardwood floors, gas fireplace, a 250-gal saltwater aquarium and access to spacious, covered deck. The kitchen has new stainless appliances, granite countertops and wood cabinets with tons of storage. Primary suite is on the main featuring trey ceilings, hardwoods floors and access to the rear deck. Primary bath has 2 sinks, jetted tub, glass/tile shower as well as a spacious walk-in closet. Upstairs there is a bonus room, spacious walk-in attic storage, 2 bedrooms with shared bath as well as a guest suite with private bath. The terrace level features a large theater room, workshop space with plumbing for a basement bath, mechanical room, and outdoor access. Owners have made a lot of improvements. See list in file. Additional property features include private well, fiber optic internet, whole home filtration, solar with backup power, beautiful waterfall, cedar closet and radon mitigation system. Attention Veterans: Assumable low interest rate VA loan on property.
